---
title: Seared Pork & Caramelised Onion Sauce with Veggie Fries & Radish Salad
description: Seasoned, seared and sliced, this pork is too good to pass up on a chance to show it off. Serve with veggie fries and a
caramelised onion sauce over the top to get those mouths watering. Bring it home with a peppery radish salad!

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
